[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.4,
    "text": "Do you think it's better to eat less meat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.4,
    "endTime": 9.209999999999999,
    "text": "I love animals a lot, but when it comes to chicken, I do not give them mercy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.21,
    "endTime": 11.189,
    "text": "I want, I will just eat them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.0,
    "endTime": 20.9,
    "text": "-Hi. -What's your name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.878,
    "endTime": 21.5,
    "text": "Phoebe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.5,
    "endTime": 23.064,
    "text": "-Helena. -Ethan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.064,
    "endTime": 24.565,
    "text": "-And you two are twins? -Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.565,
    "endTime": 25.398,
    "text": "What kind of food do you like?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.29,
    "endTime": 27.689,
    "text": "Chicken nuggets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.69,
    "endTime": 28.450000000000003,
    "text": "Beef."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.45,
    "endTime": 29.602,
    "text": "Ribs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.602,
    "endTime": 32.11,
    "text": "-Do you eat meat? -Sometimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.11,
    "endTime": 35.78,
    "text": "Like, I don't eat chicken because we have chickens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.78,
    "endTime": 38.32,
    "text": "-I have no mercy for the chickens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.32,
    "endTime": 40.1,
    "text": "I will just eat them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.1,
    "endTime": 47.382000000000005,
    "text": "- I've eaten ostrich, alligator, chitlins, cow tongue, all of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 51.21,
    "text": "[Quorn {Meatless Nuggets}.]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.21,
    "endTime": 53.79,
    "text": "-Chicken nuggets. -Yeah, chicken nuggets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.79,
    "endTime": 55.449999999999996,
    "text": "Have you ever had a chicken nugget before?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.45,
    "endTime": 57.067,
    "text": "- Yeah. - Oh yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.067,
    "endTime": 59.14,
    "text": "They're a pretty common American food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.14,
    "endTime": 61.013,
    "text": "Time to taste."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.32,
    "endTime": 67.002,
    "text": "Very crispy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.002,
    "endTime": 70.61999999999999,
    "text": "Kind of tastes like a frozen chicken nugget."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.62,
    "endTime": 75.119,
    "text": "-Like, you know, and then, like,  you  put it in the oven or something like that. -Yeah, that's exactly what we did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.21,
    "text": "This one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.21,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "That is meatless chicken nuggets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 86.292,
    "text": "And why does it have that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.292,
    "endTime": 87.5,
    "text": "That's not meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.65,
    "endTime": 92.10000000000001,
    "text": "You little liars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.75,
    "endTime": 93.482,
    "text": "How dare you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.483,
    "endTime": 95.093,
    "text": "How dare you trick us!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.093,
    "endTime": 96.9,
    "text": "We're you tricked? Did it taste like real chicken?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.9,
    "endTime": 97.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.5,
    "endTime": 100.18,
    "text": "There's no chicken in those chicken nuggets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.18,
    "endTime": 101.85700000000001,
    "text": "It's in the name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.857,
    "endTime": 104.657,
    "text": "Nobody hurt animals to go through this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.54,
    "text": "It tastes good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.54,
    "endTime": 111.293,
    "text": "That's derived from a natural fungus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.293,
    "endTime": 112.897,
    "text": "Like a foot fungus?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.897,
    "endTime": 114.30000000000001,
    "text": "No, not from a foot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.3,
    "endTime": 116.524,
    "text": "How many cows do you think you've eaten?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "None."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "You've eaten cow cause' you've had hamburgers, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 123.4,
    "text": "Oh yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.4,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "How many animals do you think you've eaten?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 127.82,
    "text": "Maybe a few hundred."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.82,
    "endTime": 133.619,
    "text": "Around, like, millions in a year because bacon every breakfast, maybe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.619,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "- No, oh yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "[Vegan \"shrimp\" cocktail.]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 141.34,
    "text": "I don't like shrimp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.34,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "It's just that I'm allergic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 145.593,
    "text": "This is amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.43,
    "endTime": 149.15300000000002,
    "text": "I've never eaten shrimp before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.153,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "-That's not real shrimp. -Hmm?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "You're in luck  because that's not real shrimp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.0,
    "endTime": 161.02,
    "text": "- Three thumbs up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.02,
    "endTime": 162.82000000000002,
    "text": "These don't even taste like real shrimp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.82,
    "endTime": 163.89,
    "text": "Not even close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.89,
    "endTime": 167.29199999999997,
    "text": "It looks very much like real shrimp, but tastes horrible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.292,
    "endTime": 170.65,
    "text": "What do you think is the cutest animal you've eaten?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.65,
    "endTime": 171.23000000000002,
    "text": "Salmon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.23,
    "endTime": 173.95,
    "text": "They're not cute, but they taste delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.95,
    "endTime": 176.33999999999997,
    "text": "But I love dogs, but why would we eat dogs?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.34,
    "endTime": 178.109,
    "text": "It'd be disgusting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.11,
    "endTime": 179.4,
    "text": "Some people do, Helena."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.4,
    "endTime": 183.95000000000002,
    "text": "[BBQ jackfruit pulled \"pork\" sandwich.] -Is this a chicken bread?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.95,
    "endTime": 187.313,
    "text": "I got a feeling this is a substitute for pork."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.313,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Go ahead and take a big bite of that BBQ pulled pork slider."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.927,
    "endTime": 196.76,
    "text": "Mm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.76,
    "endTime": 198.32,
    "text": "Absolute rubbish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.32,
    "endTime": 200.123,
    "text": "Tastes nothing like meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.123,
    "endTime": 202.0,
    "text": "Are you gonna become a vegetarian now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.0,
    "endTime": 203.933,
    "text": "- What does that even mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.933,
    "endTime": 206.62,
    "text": "it means you don't eat any meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.62,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "I don't want to become a vegetarian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.0,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "That is young jackfruit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.0,
    "endTime": 212.618,
    "text": "I love jackfruit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.618,
    "endTime": 214.917,
    "text": "Ooh, it's humongous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.917,
    "endTime": 216.67,
    "text": "Beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.67,
    "endTime": 218.625,
    "text": "And it's so heavy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.95,
    "endTime": 222.10899999999998,
    "text": "How could you guys carry this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.109,
    "endTime": 224.60000000000002,
    "text": "A fair number of people die every year from jackfruit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.6,
    "endTime": 227.56199999999998,
    "text": "- What? - How? -From it falling on their heads."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.562,
    "endTime": 228.395,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.395,
    "endTime": 233.89000000000001,
    "text": "[Quorn {Meatless Grounds & Meatballs}.]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.89,
    "endTime": 236.683,
    "text": "- Meatballs? -Yeah, spaghetti and meatballs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.683,
    "endTime": 238.423,
    "text": "But it's a fake one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.423,
    "endTime": 241.67000000000002,
    "text": "I don't know. Why don't you try it and tell me if you think it's real or fake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.67,
    "endTime": 243.35899999999998,
    "text": "You don't know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.596,
    "endTime": 246.20000000000002,
    "text": "Four thumbs up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.2,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "This tastes really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.0,
    "endTime": 249.48,
    "text": "Real meat or is it meatless."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.48,
    "endTime": 252.88199999999998,
    "text": "-No, it's meat. -It's meatless."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.882,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "And it's meatless."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 263.21,
    "text": "It looks the same, it tastes the same, so what's the point of making a substitute of meat when there's always going to be meat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.21,
    "endTime": 265.46,
    "text": "There's always going to be cows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.46,
    "endTime": 268.387,
    "text": "Maybe they want to keep the cow, not kill the cow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.387,
    "endTime": 276.808,
    "text": "According to the United Nations, the number of industrial livestock sent to slaughter each year is equivalent to eight times the human population."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.808,
    "endTime": 277.641,
    "text": "- What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 280.027,
    "text": "This just turned very sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.027,
    "endTime": 283.08799999999997,
    "text": "Do you think it's better to eat less meat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.088,
    "endTime": 286.67100000000005,
    "text": "- Yeah, but I do not care for the chickens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.671,
    "endTime": 290.0,
    "text": "[Banana Blossom \"Fish\" Taco.']"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.0,
    "endTime": 291.7,
    "text": "Is this real fish?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.7,
    "endTime": 294.0,
    "text": "Are you allergic to fish?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.0,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "Would you die if you ate fish?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 299.0,
    "text": "-I don't know. -Dive right in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.0,
    "endTime": 303.0,
    "text": "-Do we have an EpiPen here? -No, I don't have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.0,
    "endTime": 307.022,
    "text": "That's actually kind of good, like the breading, it's really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.022,
    "endTime": 309.34999999999997,
    "text": "Was that your first fish taco?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.35,
    "endTime": 310.18300000000005,
    "text": "I think so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.183,
    "endTime": 312.0,
    "text": "It's not real fish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.0,
    "endTime": 313.923,
    "text": "I always knew it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.45,
    "endTime": 318.0,
    "text": "So, that is actually dog meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.0,
    "endTime": 319.0,
    "text": "Ew!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.0,
    "endTime": 322.967,
    "text": "We can't eat dog meat in the US, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.967,
    "endTime": 328.0,
    "text": "So that there is fried banana blossom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.0,
    "endTime": 329.8,
    "text": "Do you want to see what it looks like?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.8,
    "endTime": 331.0,
    "text": "- No, don't touch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.0,
    "endTime": 332.133,
    "text": "Is it alive?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.133,
    "endTime": 336.53999999999996,
    "text": "No... I'm kidding, it's alive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.54,
    "endTime": 341.5,
    "text": "They do actually look like bananas, but I don't like the brown color."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.5,
    "endTime": 344.583,
    "text": "Who's going to eat this poor banana blossom?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.583,
    "endTime": 347.39000000000004,
    "text": "Well, it's already been taken off the branch. It's dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.41,
    "endTime": 348.223,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.223,
    "endTime": 351.45,
    "text": "Would you feel worse for a fish or a banana blossom?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.45,
    "endTime": 352.52,
    "text": "Banana blossom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.52,
    "endTime": 355.633,
    "text": "I mean, sharks are going to eat fish anyways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.633,
    "endTime": 357.57,
    "text": "So what did you learn today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.57,
    "endTime": 360.0,
    "text": "These things are fake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.0,
    "endTime": 362.0,
    "text": "Is it okay to eat meat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.0,
    "endTime": 362.88,
    "text": "Sometimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.88,
    "endTime": 364.5,
    "text": "I mean, you have to have a balance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.5,
    "endTime": 366.85,
    "text": "Salads, you could put meat in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.85,
    "endTime": 369.0,
    "text": "-You could put bacon. - Chicken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.0,
    "endTime": 374.88,
    "text": "You can put whatever you want in the salad, and it'd be vegetarian, and it'd be meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.88,
    "endTime": 377.563,
    "text": "Because everything goes with meat and chicken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.563,
    "endTime": 380.53999999999996,
    "text": "Would you ever cut down on the meat you eat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.54,
    "endTime": 381.83000000000004,
    "text": "Maybe one day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.83,
    "endTime": 386.4,
    "text": "I would probably stop eating all the other meats, but I can't stop eating chickens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.4,
    "endTime": 388.313,
    "text": "Chickens are just so good."
  }
]